705043f-a.title: Brooklyn: Humboldt Street - Scholes Street
705043f-a.text:

October 25, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.

706680f-a.title: Brooklyn: Scholes Street - Humboldt Street
706680f-a.text:
Scholes Street, north side, between Humboldt Street (left) and Bush.
wick Ave. (right). These buildings were later demolished (1935) to
Mmake way for Federal low rental apartments.
September 1935.
P. L. Sperr.

706685f-b.title: Brooklyn: Scholes Street - Humboldt Street
706685f-b.text:
(1)
195-201 Scholes Street, north side, east from Humboldt Street.
Also seen is Humboldt Street, east side, north from Scholes Street.
October 25, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same; as seen from west of Humboldt Street, showing the site
after clearance for a Federal housing project. The buildings in the
right background are on Bushwick ive.; the steeples at the left, are on
St. Margaret's Hospital.
December 22, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
